Class TicketListFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • in.teramatrix.flint.driver.fragment.TicketListFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.support.v4.widget.SwipeRefreshLayout.OnRefreshListener, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, com.malinskiy.superrecyclerview.OnMoreListener, okhttp3.Callback

    public class TicketListFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements okhttp3.Callback, android.support.v4.widget.SwipeRefreshLayout.OnRefreshListener, com.malinskiy.superrecyclerview.OnMoreListener
    A list fragment of closed and open tickets. Here's a SuperRecyclerView has been populated to show all closed/open tickets. The response of api call also handled in this class using Callback's onFailure() & onResponse().

    Author:
    Mohsin Khan
    Date:
    14/9/2016
